item.title: What was the first RSPS?
item.dc:creator: @n33bz0rpl0x `Aaron
item.description:
@n33bz0rpl0x wrote:

[quote=“snoopy89, post:35, topic:345850”][quote author=Newty link=topic=442230.msg3251837#msg3251837 date=1277824016]

WinterLove was a RSC server if im currect.

Nah the first RSC server was released well after the wL server. I can’t remember who made it though? Reines maybe, xEnt will correct me if I’m wrong.

It wasn’t Reines, maby baketool or whatever it as called.

Bakatool worked on RS2 private servers, ub3r server 3.0 (dodian)
[/quote]

RSClassic went first I belive, or was the first server a rs2? if so I have no idea what was the first one.

I wrote some history about RSCDaemon here: http://www.rscemulation.net/about.html

“The source code originally started life as RSCDaemon, a project that eXemplar, Sean and Philodespotos contributed to but unfortunately never got to a state that would be considered playable. Reines decided to picked up where they left off and turned it into an actual private server simular to RSCEmulation. After a good run JAGeX shut RSCDaemon down, the source code got leaked and mass private servers were born. Since then the source code has been drastically modified, improved and developed further to turn it into what you know as RSCEmulation.”

I got that information from eXemplar, xEnt, PR4Y, etc.

Hi mate, no one really gives a shit about RSC in this section, including myself. I’m not trying to be rude but can you get your fucking ass out of this section, thanks man we really only (most of us) give a shit about RS2(RSPS, and if that).

This is free for all, and he didn’t say what was the first rs2 server out. So I belive you have the right to shut the f*ck up.[/quote]

Hi snoopy, So i believe you should shut the fuck up, not f*ck.

Read full topic

item.title: What was the first RSPS?
item.dc:creator: @doom_j doom_j
item.description:
@doom_j wrote:

Since some one deleted my post that answered this thread I will post it again.

http://runewiki.moparisthebest.com/index.php?title=Private_Server

Wl (WinterLove) - only released 1 server, it was the original server and only one made at the time. It was basically the Cryption, Stream, Server classes. You could log in and just run around that’s it you didn’t see your self but the items on the ground.

BlakeScape was the first server to be released with the basic features like walking, multi player, rendering, etc.
